sources.name: Source
sources.query: integral(sum(ts("aws.lambda.duration.sum", not FunctionName=* and Region=*)))

sources.name: Source
sources.query: integral(sum(ts("aws.lambda.invocations.sum", not FunctionName=* and Region=*)))

sources.name: Source
sources.query: integral(sum(ts("aws.lambda.errors.sum", not FunctionName=* and Region=*)))

sources.name: Source
sources.query: integral(sum(ts("aws.lambda.throttles.sum", not FunctionName=* and Region=*)))

sources.name: Function
sources.query: sum(ts("aws.lambda.duration.average", FunctionName=* and Resource=* and Region=*), FunctionName, sources)

sources.name: Function
sources.query: sum(ts("aws.lambda.invocations.sum", FunctionName=* and Resource=* and Region=*), FunctionName, sources)

sources.name: Function
sources.query: sum(ts("aws.lambda.errors.sum", FunctionName=* and Resource=* and Region=*), FunctionName, sources)

sources.name: Execution Time
sources.query: align(1m, sum(ts("aws.lambda.duration.sum", FunctionName=* and Resource=* and Region=*), FunctionName, sources))

sources.name: Invocations
sources.query: align(1m, sum(ts("aws.lambda.invocations.sum", FunctionName=* and Resource=* and Region=*), FunctionName, sources))

sources.name: Errors
sources.query: align(1m, sum(ts("aws.lambda.errors.sum", FunctionName=* and Resource=* and Region=*), FunctionName, sources))

sources.name: Usage
sources.query: sum(ts("aws.lambda.duration.sum", FunctionName=${a_function} and Resource=* and Region=*)) / 1000 / 60 / ${b_factor} * 100

sources.name: Source
sources.query: integral(sum(ts("aws.lambda.duration.sum", FunctionName=${a_function} and Resource=* and Region=*)))

sources.name: Source
sources.query: integral(sum(ts("aws.lambda.invocations.sum", FunctionName=${a_function} and Resource=* and Region=*)))

sources.name: Source
sources.query: integral(sum(ts("aws.lambda.errors.sum", FunctionName=${a_function} and Resource=* and Region=*)))

sources.name: Source
sources.query: integral(sum(ts("aws.lambda.throttles.sum", FunctionName=${a_function} and Resource=* and Region=*)))

sources.name: Usage
sources.query: sum(ts("aws.lambda.duration.sum", FunctionName=${a_function} and Resource=* and Region=*)) / 1000 / 60 / ${b_factor} * 100

sources.name: Usage yesterday
sources.query: lag(1d, ${Usage})

sources.name: Usage last week
sources.query: lag(1w, ${Usage})

sources.sourceDescription: This query is ready made to be converted to an alert when the Usage is 80% or greater. Click the Create Alert link below.
sources.name: Alert Ready
sources.query: ${Usage} >= 80

sources.sourceDescription: This query is ready made to be converted to an alert when the rate of change of the usage compared to last week is 50% or greater.  Click the Create Alert link below.
sources.name: Alert Ready (rate of change)
sources.query: between(${Usage} / ${Usage last week}, 0.5, 1.5) != 1

sources.name: Duration
sources.query: align(1m, sum(ts("aws.lambda.duration.sum", FunctionName=${a_function} and Resource=* and Region=*)))

sources.name: Duration RoC
sources.query: (${Duration} - mavg(30m, ${Duration})) / sqrt(mvar(30m, ${Duration}))

sources.name: Invocations
sources.query: align(1m, sum(ts("aws.lambda.invocations.sum", FunctionName=${a_function} and Resource=* and Region=*)))

sources.name: Invocations RoC
sources.query: (${Invocations} - mavg(30m, ${Invocations})) / sqrt(mvar(30m, ${Invocations}))

sources.name: Duration
sources.query: avg(ts("aws.lambda.duration.average", FunctionName=${a_function} and Resource=* and Region=*))

sources.name: Invocations
sources.query: avg(ts("aws.lambda.invocations.sum", FunctionName=${a_function} and Resource=* and Region=*))

sources.name: Concurrent executions
sources.query: ${Duration} * ${Invocations} / 1000 / 60

sources.name: Minimum
sources.query: align(1m, min, ts("aws.lambda.duration.minimum", FunctionName=${a_function} and Resource=* and Region=*))

sources.name: Average
sources.query: align(1m, mean, ts("aws.lambda.duration.average", FunctionName=${a_function} and Resource=* and Region=*))

sources.name: Maximum
sources.query: align(1m, max, ts("aws.lambda.duration.maximum", FunctionName=${a_function} and Resource=* and Region=*))

sources.name: Invocations
sources.query: align(1m, sum, ts("aws.lambda.invocations.sum", FunctionName=${a_function} and Resource=* and Region=*))

sources.sourceDescription: This query is ready made to be converted to an alert when this function receives no invocations (potential outage) over a 10 minute period or greater. Click the Create Alert link below.
sources.name: Alert Ready
sources.query: msum(10m, ${Invocations}) = 0

sources.name: Errors
sources.query: align(1m, sum, ts("aws.lambda.errors.sum", FunctionName=${a_function} and Resource=* and Region=*))

sources.sourceDescription: This query is ready made to be converted to an alert when this function receives generates 25 errors or more over a 10 minute period. Click the Create Alert link below.
sources.name: Alert Ready
sources.query: msum(10m, ${Errors}) >= 25

sources.name: Throttled
sources.query: align(1m, sum, ts("aws.lambda.throttles.sum", FunctionName=${a_function} and Resource=* and Region=*))

sources.sourceDescription: This query is ready made to be converted to an alert when this function is throttled 50 times or more over a 10 minute period. Click the Create Alert link below.
sources.name: Alert Ready
sources.query: msum(10m, ${Throttled}) >= 50
